description: Incredible opportunity new construction smart homes in S. Boston! Spacious floor through layouts with over 1,200 sq ft of expansive living space all on one level. No expense spared here with Custom Italian kitchens designed by Samantha DeMarco of Devine Design Center, oversized windows, beautiful white oak hardwood flooring throughout, facial recognition entry systems, tastefully designed contemporary bathrooms with glass shower stalls, and vanities done in the same custom finish as kitchens. The condos will come with a wall mounted Ipad system for owners to control everything from their lighting to their heating and cooling. Tons of storage, extra thick molding and stylish doors and hardware.  You can feel the quality of the craftsmanship, and the thoughtfulness of the design throughout. Deeded garage parking with EV charging capabilities too!  All at an amazing location just a block from the Andrew Square T stop, with new restaurants and bars, and easy access to I-93 and I-90.
